 Carbonfree Certified

 ClimeCo Certified

 About this item 
                     
      
  •  CUSTOMIZABLE SLEEP ROUTINE- Dreamegg Sunrise 1 is the perfect solution to customize your morning wake-up routine and night sleep routine, gradually improving your sleep cycle. With the combination of simulated sunlight and nature sounds, this sunrise alarm clock sound machine makes every wake-up and wind-down soothing and stress-relieving, letting you feel like you're in nature.  
    •   
  •  WAKE UP GENTLY- Dreamegg Sunrise 1 enables you to have a better morning wake-up experience with natural comfort. Customizing your sunrise alarm clock, wake up naturally to a simulated sunrise and soothing natural sounds. No more jarring alarm blasts or fighting to get up. Say goodbye to groggy mornings!  
    •   
  •  SLEEP COMFORTABLY- As a white noise sound machine, Dreamegg Sunrise 1 is perfect for adults, kids and babies to relax and sleep. It is equipped with 29 soothing sounds including nature sounds, meditations, lullabies, white noise, brown noise, pink noise and fan sounds. High-quality sounds immerses you quickly in a cozy and tranquil environment, helping you drift into deep sleep faster.  
    •   
  •  DIMMABLE NIGHT LIGHT- With 9 stunning colors and adjustable brightness, the night light of Dreamegg Sunrise 1 can be controlled independently. Choose your favorite nightlight color on this alarm clock sound machine and chill out to comforting sounds as you wind down for bed.  
    •   
  •  PHONE-FREE SETUP- Dreamegg Sunrise 1 alarm clock for bedrooms is easy to set up. There is no need for any device connection. You can directly set your sunrise alarm clock or white noise sound machine functions right on the device. Its hand-sized diameter makes it perfect for travel. Phone-free setup allows you to put down your phone and truly enjoy the joy of the journey!  
    •   
  •  BEDSIDE ESSENTIAL- Dreamegg Sunrise 1 is crafted with a cotton-linen fabric, soft and gentle on the skin. this sunrise alarm clock sound machine is the ideal sleep companion and delicate gift choice for your bedrooms, really a bedside essential. What's more, the high-quality customer service of Dreamegg will save you worry and brings your smile back on face to ensure your purchase and trust.

 How does Dreamegg Sunrise 1 change Your Life? 
    
 
 
                                      
 
                                        
 Sleep Soundly 
    
 
                                   
 Equipped with 29 soothing sounds of high quality, Dreamegg Sunrise 1 can immerse you quickly in a cozy and tranquil environment to help you fall asleep faster and better. It includes 8 nature sounds, 5 baby sounds, 2 meditation sounds, 2 brown noise, 2 white noise, 3 pink noise and 7 fan sounds. 
    
 
 
                                      
 
                                        
 Wake up Energized 
    
 
                                   
 With the combination of simulated sunlight and nature sounds, Dreamegg Sunrise 1 makes you feel as if youre waking up in nature to the glowing sunlight and soothing nature sounds. No more jarring alarm blasts or fighting to get up. Say goodbye to groggy mornings!

     Do I have to download an application to use Dreamegg Sunrise 1? 
        
                                      
                            
    
                                                              
     No! Dreamegg Sunrise 1 doesnt require any connection. Just plug it in and enjoy anywhere, anytime. Its perfect for hotels, schools, or home use! 
        
    • 
                         
  • 
                            
    
                                
                                                                      
     Is this just a sunrise wake up light? 
        
                                      
                            
    
                                                              
     No, Dreamegg Sunrise 1 combines a sunrise alarm, sound machine, bedside light, and dimmable clock to help you cultivate sleep and wake routines, building a healthy sleep-wake cycle, especially great for those who work nights and sleep during the day. 
        
    • 
                         
  • 
                            
    
                                
                                                                      
     Can I travel with it? 
        
                                      
                            
    
                                                              
     Sure, Dreamegg Sunrise 1 is about 5.91 inches in diameter (the size of an adult palm) and 2.87 inches thick. It comes with a power adapter, making it ideal for travel or to take on business trips. 
        
    • 
                         
  • 
                            
    
                                
                                                                      
     Is it difficult to use? 
        
                                      
                            
    
                                                              
     No, Dreamegg Sunrise 1 is easy to use, and theres a how-to video on this listing (in the images below the title) for your reference. If you have any issues, just reach out to Dreamegg team, a satisfactory solution will be provided within 24 hours.

Directions
    
1. Power on the device by pressing the 'Power' button. 2. To select a sound, press the 'Sound' button and use the '+' and '-' buttons to scroll through the 29 available sounds. 3. Adjust the volume using the '+' and '-' buttons on the side of the device. 4. To set a timer, press the 'Timer' button and use the '+' and '-' buttons to select the desired duration (15, 30, 60, or 90 minutes). 5. To adjust the brightness of the night light, press the 'Light' button and use the '+' and '-' buttons to select the desired brightness level. 6. To customize the sunrise alarm, press the 'Sunrise' button and use the '+' and '-' buttons to adjust the duration of the sunrise simulation (15, 30, 45, or 60 minutes).

                    Dreamegg Sunrise 1   

  Why do you need a Dreamegg Sunrise 1? 
 Dreamegg Sunrise 1 is the perfect solution to customize your morning wake-up routine and night sleep routine, gradually improving your sleep cycle. 
 With the combination of simulated sunlight and nature sounds, this sunrise alarm clock sound machine makes every wake-up and wind-down soothing and stress-relieving, letting you feel like you're in nature.

  How Dreamegg Sunrise 1 Makes a Difference for You 
 1. Wake up naturally to a simulated sunrise and soothing natural sounds. No more jarring alarm blasts or fighting to get up. Say goodbye to groggy mornings!
 2. Equipped with 29 soothing sounds including nature sounds, meditations, lullabies, white noise, brown noise, pink noise and fan sounds, Dreamegg Sunrise 1 is perfect for adults, kids and babies to relax and sleep. 
 3. With 9 stunning colors and adjustable brightness, the night light of Dreamegg Sunrise 1 can be controlled independently. 
 4. There is no need for any device connection. You can directly set your sunrise alarm clock or white noise sound machine functions right on the device.
 5. Dreamegg Sunrise 1 is crafted with a cotton-linen fabric, green and gentle on the skin, an ideal sleep companion and delicate gift choice for bedside!
